# Allowlisting gitignore template for GO projects prevents us
# from adding various unwanted local files, such as generated
# files, developer configurations or IDE-specific files etc.
#
# Recommended: Go.AllowList.gitignore

# Ignore everything
*

# Re-include non-hidden directories so allowlisted files in subdirectories
# can still be discovered.
!*/

# But not these files...
!/.gitignore
!/AGENTS.md

!*.go
!go.sum
!go.mod

!README.md
!LICENSE
!skills-lock.json

# Project docs
!/docs/**/*.md

# Public skills
!/skills/**/*.md

# Hidden directories must be allowlisted explicitly.
!/.agents/**/*.md
!/.agents/**/*.yaml
!/.agents/**/*.yml

# !Makefile

# ...even if they are in subdirectories
!*/
